ities for humor, emotion and earnest questioning. What would our younger selves think of our lives now? Would they even recognize us? She explores these questions with tenderness and sympathy for both Alices, younger and older.  This companion of What Alice Forgot offers the following: • A detailed Book Review from Experts • Helps you pick up bits you might have missed as we decipher the novel. • Details of Characters &amp; Key Character Analysis • Summary of the text, with some analytical comments interspersed • A plot Analysis of What Alice Forgot that will make you see the book from another angle • Discussion &amp; Analysis of Themes, Symbols… • And Much More for YOU to Discover!  This Analysis of What Alice Forgot fills the gap, making you understand more while enhancing your reading experience.<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"6891442937667480495\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'15_book_23790817\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"KCA8f3Jg4vS82gQmioFDQNZPPcJRMJWHrxG9OldGddXyPdiRoToLV1C0E8D9gdz/m/zunmIfjEUdy4+uAStXYg==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"23790817\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"15_book_23790817\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" v